plot: On a trip to Iceland for Kanye's music video shoot over Kourtney's birthday weekend, Kim finds herself spread too thin as she tries to cater to both her sister and her husband. Meanwhile, Scott debates surprising Kourtney by showing up in Iceland, and Lamar tries to mend Khloé and Rob's relationship.

Kim and Kanye are going to Iceland to shoot Kanye's new video and he gets upset when Kim misses the shoot. Scott considers surprising Kourtney by going to Iceland for her birthday. Lamar tries to help Khloe repair her relationship with Rob.
